name: Daniel Rey Cimafranca
text: Masyado kasi maraming magagaling na habol lang patunayang tama sila at ipamukha sa iba na mali sila hehehehe It shouldnt be just about being right, they also need to reach out and be convincing.  A failure of IQ maybe?  Nagkulang cguro sa EQ
